        Constructs a DiagnosticImpl (such as an error, warning, or information item) using generic Java Objects as source and sourceField.
        Parameters:
        severity - The severity of the diagnostic. One of Diagnostic.INFO, Diagnostic.WARNING or Diagnostic.ERROR.
        uic - the current user's UIContext
        source - the component which the diagnostic relates to.
        message - the message to display to the user, using MessageFormat syntax.
        args - optional arguments for the message format string.
